{
  "name": "subs_4",  
  "captions": [
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- In this form,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:06.510"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "I know it's not a child yet,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:08.190"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "in the sense it does not\nsmile at the sight of a parent",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:10.980"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "or a little wind.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:15.540"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "It cannot wrap its whole hand\naround one's little finger,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:17.520"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "and it cannot stare into its eyes and see.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:23.010"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "But it has all the potential",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:27.600"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "to be smaller than a millimetre.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:28.890"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "Yet it has all the\ninstructions it needs to grow",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:32.070"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "and become the life we desire.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:35.670"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "This does not.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:52.560"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "No, you do not need to say.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:59.400"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "This knowledge has come\nabout because of this scan?",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:07.230"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- It has.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:09.810"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- Could we have found this another way?",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:11.250"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- Possibly.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:13.530"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "But there would likely be\nno hope in that knowledge,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:15.450"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "only pain.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:20.910"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- For all this knowledge,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:26.130"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "it's still a fact",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:28.140"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "that not all pregnancies go\nthe way one expects or wants.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:30.090"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "And how unbelievable joy can\nturn to unbelievable sadness,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:36.930"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "for it has always been the case",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:43.680"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "that some life will shine and fade",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:45.360"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "without anyone knowing they ever existed.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:48.990"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "Some life will fade out of choice,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:52.560"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "others against the will\nof expecting parents,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:55.770"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "nearly always without fault or blame.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:00.690"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "It's as painful an experience",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:04.920"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "as one could imagine at life\nnot lived ended far too soon.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:06.900"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "A pain many of us have shared.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:13.920"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "A pain there's been very\nlittle we could do to prevent",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:17.010"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "and know what we might do to change that.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:22.320"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- I know the pain you talk of.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:28.380"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "And coming through it,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:33.930"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "I know that was a path I\nand they had to travel.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:37.560"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- Given the choice,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:43.650"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "would you have wanted to\ntry and save their life?",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:45.330"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- I think at the time,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:51.930"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "I would've done anything\nto hold him in my arms.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:56.190"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "But,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:02.460"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "I've come to terms with the fact",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:05.490"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "that it was a life that\nwas not meant to be.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:07.020"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "However much I wanted it to live,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:12.510"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "its path was not that.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:16.500"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "And with time,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:19.710"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "I've learned to accept the fact",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:22.650"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "that that's just a part of life.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:23.970"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- But with genetic engineering,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:27.840"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "there may have been\nsomething we could have done.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:31.080"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- But still.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:33.510"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "I'm not sure I could have gone that far.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:36.270"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- Think of it like life-saving surgery.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:39.240"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "You would not deny a\nchild that, would you?",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:42.420"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- But I don't think those\ntwo things are the same.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:45.180"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- No, not exactly, but\nboth are interventions.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:48.330"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "Say instead of a metal scalpel",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:53.910"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "and a special patch to\nrepair a hole in one's heart,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:56.010"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "coded RNA seeks and replaces\nerrors in our genetic code",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:59.310"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "to intervene before a\nhole could even form.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:04.080"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "It cannot save every life,\nbut for those that it can...",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:08.040"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- It's not as if you're\ncorrecting something",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:11.400"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "that you hold in your hands.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:13.470"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "You're changing what that\nchild was meant to be,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:15.990"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "and altering that feels like...",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:19.890"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- Like we are altering their destiny.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:26.325"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- Like all interventions do.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:28.950"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "Remember, we are simply\ntweaking their code",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:31.680"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "to ensure they have a chance of life.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:34.320"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "We are changing nothing\nthat can't already exist.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:37.020"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- I don't believe that to be true.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:41.280"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "I think instinctively,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:44.100"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "you might want to do everything you could,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:45.720"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "but it might not be one simple\nintervention that does it.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:47.520"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "You might end up changing\nthe child in so many ways.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:53.280"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "It brings into question at what point",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:57.350"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "it's still the child you conceived.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:59.220"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- What wrong could be done to a life",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:05:01.320"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "if its alternative is no life at all?",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:05:03.360"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- It's not that.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:05:06.900"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "It's not a straightforward a question",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:05:09.870"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "as you make it out to be.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:05:11.278"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "And I just wonder.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:05:15.090"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "Is that a fair ask",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:05:17.940"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "of a parent for a child\nthat was not destined to be?",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:05:20.370"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- When it might be the\nonly thing we could do",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:05:25.110"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "to save their life,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:05:27.720"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "I don't think we have\na choice except to ask.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:05:30.030"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- Nothing would stop\nme from saying, \"Yes.\"",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:05:34.290"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- Could there be",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:05:39.270"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "a more delicate question than this?",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:05:40.560"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "Although we refer to\nthis as an unborn child,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:05:44.610"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "it is both a child, not a child,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:05:49.920"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "and an intervention in\nsuch a natural process,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:05:53.820"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "however painful, is...",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:05:58.200"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "Please if you can, I'd like to know",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:06:07.020"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "if you would be willing\nto use genetic engineering",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:06:11.610"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "to attempt to save your unborn child",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:06:15.270"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "if it was the only option.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:06:18.630"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "Even if that meant\nchanging the very nature",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:06:21.203"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "of what that child was meant to be.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:06:24.840"
      }
    ]
  }